hist bombs on Broadway\"</a>. The Guardian<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">29 July</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=David+Mamet%27s+The+Anarchist+bombs+on+Broadway&amp;rft.date=2012-12-05&amp;rft.au=Trueman&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fculture%2F2012%2Fdec%2F05%2Fdavid-mamet-anarchist-broadway&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Anarchist+%28play%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2012/dec/05/david-mamet-anarchist-broadway\">https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2012/dec/05/david-mamet-anarchist-broadway</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-teatroespanol.es-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-teatroespanol.es_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-teatroespanol.es_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://teatroespanol.es/descargas/dossier_la_anarquista%5B2%5D.pdf\">http://teatroespanol.es/descargas/dossier_la_anarquista%5B2%5D.pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://cultura.elpais.com/cultura/2013/01/14/actualidad/1358180341_938232.html\">http://cultura.elpais.com/cultura/2013/01/14/actualidad/1358180341_938232.html</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ng-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ng_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Ng, David (9 March 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/arts/culture/la-et-cm-anarchist-david-mamet-felicity-huffman-rebecca-pidgeon-20150309-story.html\">\"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">'</span>The Anarchist' by David Mamet coming to L.A. with Felicity Huffman\"</a>. Los Angeles Times<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">29 July</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=%27The+Anarchist%27+by+David+Mamet+coming+to+L.A.+with+Felicity+Huffman&amp;rft.date=2015-03-09&amp;rft.aulast=Ng&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Farts%2Fculture%2Fla-et-cm-anarchist-david-mamet-felicity-huffman-rebecca-pidgeon-20150309-story.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Anarchist+%28play%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Grossberg, Michael (29 June 2017). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://digital.olivesoftware.com/Olive/ODN/ColumbusDispatch/Default.aspx\">\"The Anarchist\"</a>. <i>The Columbus Dispatch: Weekender</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">3 July</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Columbus+Dispatch%3A+Weekender&amp;rft.atitle=The+Anarchist&amp;rft.date=2017-06-29&amp;rft.aulast=Grossberg&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdigital.olivesoftware.com%2FOlive%2FODN%2FColumbusDispatch%2FDefault.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Anarchist+%28play%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></sp